00:10:26.635 --> 00:10:27.682
flexor-extensor.

00:10:27.682 --> 00:10:29.378
You see the hips are coming up,

00:10:29.378 --> 00:10:30.699
the legs are coming up.

00:10:30.699 --> 00:10:33.327
The arms are extending, and then briefly

00:10:33.327 --> 00:10:35.130
adducting to the midline.

00:10:35.130 --> 00:10:36.759
It's coming in a cluster.

00:10:36.759 --> 00:10:39.009
It's coming pretty regular.

